commit.message:
test: Replace test numbering with phases

As tests should be arranged by topic if possible, sequential numbering
would require renumbering every successive test in order to insert a
new one.  Because some tests must run before others, represent this as
three numbered groups.  The ordering within each group is unimportant,
and tests should (and currently do) pass regardless of their order
within the group.
